        "timestamp": "2020-02-28 14:27:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Merging this was little hasty, we should have had the CI job merged first, then verify this and only then merge...\n\nIs it possible to validate the CI job if the target source code isn't already merged?",
